##### build the image:
docker build -t xxxxxxx/myapp:3.0 .

### push the image on docker hub
docker push xxxxxxx/myapp:3.0

### run the from docker hub
docker run -d -p 5000:5000 xxxxxxx/myapp:3.0

## note: reaplace xxxxxxx with your dockerhub username






